Is), Louisiade Archipelago (Trobriand, Woodlark, and Misima Is), Solomon Is (Choiseul, New 
<collectingCountry box="[2475,2588,1456,1489]" name="Georgia" pageId="6" pageNumber="697">Georgia</collectingCountry>
, Mbanika, and 
<collectingCountry box="[1593,1786,1495,1528]" name="Saint Kitts and Nevis" pageId="6" pageNumber="697">San Cristobal</collectingCountry>
), 
<collectingCountry box="[1809,1927,1495,1528]" name="Vanuatu" pageId="6" pageNumber="697">Vanuatu</collectingCountry>
